    This page allow you to configure the behaviors of your forum.<br/>
    Here are in details, tab by tab,
    what is permits to do : <br/>
    <ul>
        <li><h3>General</h3>
            This tab permits to configure the globale part of your forum.
            <ul>
                <li>Give a name to your forum</li>
                <li>Provide a slogan to it</li>
                <li>Define rules of use, which if fill, will appear a link of the rules on the forum index page</li>
                <li>Put the email of the webmaster (which will be used by the mailer)</li>
                <li>Put the email of the administrator</li>
                <li>Define the time zone of the entire forum. This value could be changed by each of the member with his profile page</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><h3>Messages</h3>
            This tab permits to configure the size and number of messages,thread,replies by page.
        </li>
        <li><h3>Timeout</h3>
            This tab permits to configure the timeout of one user when he is online.
        </li>
        <li><h3>Importants threads</h3>
            This tab permits to define from the quantity of messages, if the thread is considering as important.
